'''Kallebarth Way''' was a 250-meter-long hallway onboard [[Toryaz Station]]'s [[Narsacc Habitat]]. It was directly below [[Varganner Way]]. In [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]], during negotiations with the [[Five Worlds|Corellian alliance]], it was where the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] delegates were housed.

